anyone at all.

01:58.184 --> 01:59.685
Of course, on those occasions,

01:59.686 --> 02:01.186
we don't have a party...

02:01.187 --> 02:05.691
which is probably why
no one ever shows up.

02:07.193 --> 02:08.693
You sure I look all right?

02:08.695 --> 02:11.196
Oh, you look wonderful,
darling, really.

02:11.197 --> 02:12.197
