02:12.198 --> 02:13.699
Oh, they're not gonna hate you.

02:13.700 --> 02:15.200
Whose is that?
What?

02:15.201 --> 02:16.702
That's my tie.

02:16.703 --> 02:18.203
You stole my tie.

02:18.204 --> 02:21.206
Jess, he stole my tie.

02:21.207 --> 02:23.208
Daddy, I lent him
one of your ties.

02:23.209 --> 02:25.210
That is my favorite tie.

02:25.211 --> 02:26.712
JESSICA:
Well, darling,

02:26.713 --> 02:28.714
